The whole query would be: `'INSERT INTO "characters_skillability" ("skill") VALUES (('Academics', 'Mental'))'` which is not valid.

It should be: `'INSERT INTO "characters_skillability" ("skill") VALUES (?,?)'` and unpack the tuple.

Is this possible?

